{"tid":2272010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴入嚟聽下我意見 令香港人有能力保護自己嘅方法","createTime":"2020-11-05T00:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T00:43:52.000Z","uid":370186,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c17f9794c8fdfd1652c585751f8d82cb1f1732a2","tid":2272010,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:29:22.000Z","msg":"尋日開錯咗我再開過<br />\n<br />\n我想問吓你眾籌收咁多錢<br />\n點解唔直接建立一間香港人嘅保安公司<br />\n點解仲要用啲錢去打國際線？<br />\n<br />\n只有武力先係可以保障和平嘅資本<br />\n<br />\n你可以係外國建立一間保安公司<br />\n招聘香港人流亡嘅手足令到佢哋有工作嘅地點<br />\n可以請啲退休軍人 等佢哋嚟教 就好似歐洲啲保安學院咁樣<br />\n跟住可以承接唔同嘅保安任務 等個班人有經驗<br />\n因為參軍要聽軍隊嘅命令，無辦法隨時起行<br />\n<br />\n我想講真正嘅復國 唔係靠人哋去幫助<br />\n你哋成日用嚟打飛機嘅以色列 佢哋係用血汗去守護佢哋嘅家邦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CHEc6YSF9R5/?igshid=r7ak0ov799qe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCHEc6YSF9R5%2F%3Figshid%3Dr7ak0ov799qe&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4HpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=d12ca3e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCHEc6YSF9R5%2F%3Figshid%3Dr7ak0ov799qe&h=062048fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CHEc6YSF9R5/?igshid=r7ak0ov799qe</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人講獨立已經講咗好耐 希望你哋可以踏出第一步 <br />\n<br />\n希望嗰位攬炒巴<br />\n要對得住攬炒呢個名<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">革命未成功之前只不過係暴動，我更加願意人哋稱呼我係暴徒，因為革命就係要不擇手段</span><br />\n唔好再寄望喺各國之間嘅權力鬥爭<br />\n而係寄望係自身香港人身上 只有自己足夠強大 咁就唔需要俾人可憐<br />\n<br />\n願意戰死嘅人唔多，但亦都唔少 <br />\n我哋只係爭一個機會，一個拉近武力差距嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n時代正在逐漸瘋狂<br />\n我們的命運都與時代革命交織<br />\n無人能置身事外<br />\n唯有以戰止戰 以死換生<br />\n<br />\n當一切落幕之時<br />\n還望能與爾等一同再三回味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pepiKO0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpepiKO0.jpg&h=41622465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一提嚟緊嘅11月11日 唔係一個俾你瘋狂購物嘅所謂光棍節 而係一個有特別價值嘅日子 你要給予為香港戰死嘅英靈最崇高嘅尊重<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">If I can die for my city that is my honored</span></span>"},{"pid":"ebdf1f7d0c86a89ab01accfc7f543c1e3c399405","tid":2272010,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:32:58.000Z","msg":"人地寫封信,美國政府即時停止運作<br />\n仲開保安公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bb143b96b19e69be342c51f7de8b8674d65cd3","tid":2272010,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebdf1f7d0c86a89ab01accfc7f543c1e3c399405","tid":2272010,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:32:58.000Z","msg":"人地寫封信,美國政府即時停止運作<br />\n仲開保安公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"你明唔明要迎合佢哋班人嘅取向<br />\n咁啲錢係佢度 唔用呢啲方法點樣逼佢用係有用嘅地方"},{"pid":"979cd159683b51bb72bc027705060518e220312a","tid":2272010,"uid":31765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"曬鳩氣啦<br />\n呢條撚樣咪又係獨裁<br />\n講兩句唔岩聽就block鳩人<br />\n睇清楚佢真面目啦"},{"pid":"cebaea3634bf7e9bd6c1d672c29f3b35c06b906e","tid":2272010,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdQYLCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdQYLCw.jpg&h=c1f24ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17hL94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17hL94c.jpg&h=523ef4c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0pbmaU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0pbmaU.gif&h=5e076e45&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}